        "prompt": "Create an original, non-infringing social media avatar for a content creator account focused on new energy vehicles, digital products, and lifestyle goods.\n\nStyle/medium: needs a modern, clean, universally approachable aesthetic — exact stylistic execution is yours\nComposition: must be a square avatar format with a clear focal center, visually balanced at small display sizes\nSubject: must include visual elements representing the three content pillars: new energy vehicles / digital tech / lifestyle goods — unified into a single cohesive icon or character\nScene/backdrop: needs a neutral, platform-agnostic backdrop — exact background treatment is yours\nLighting/mood: needs a friendly, energetic yet approachable atmosphere — exact light treatment is yours\nColor palette: needs a vibrant but universally safe direction — exact palette is yours\nMaterials/textures: \nText (verbatim): \nConstraints: must be culturally neutral and free of symbols, gestures, colors, or iconography that carry negative or taboo connotations in any major culture or religion; must read clearly at small avatar sizes (32px–200px)\nAvoid: must avoid religious symbols, politically sensitive imagery, culturally exclusive gestures, overly aggressive or dark tones, and any element that could alienate audiences on either Chinese or international social platforms",
